Sun Jul 10 11:39:27 EST 2005  Nathan R. Yergler <nathan@yergler.net>
  * add-behavior-library
  
  Added Behaviour javascript library.  Behaviour provides sane application of Javascript functions using CSS-style selectors.  More information on Behaviour at http://www.ripcord.co.nz/behaviour/.
  

Sun Jul 10 11:38:28 EST 2005  Nathan R. Yergler <nathan@yergler.net>
  * remove-sajax-library

Sun Jul 10 11:35:43 EST 2005  Nathan R. Yergler <nathan@yergler.net>
  * add-sack-library
  
  Added the Simple Ajax Code Kit for simple click-server AJAX communications.  This replaces the heavier, and somewhat magical, SAJAX library.
  
  More information on SACK at http://twilightuniverse.com/projects/sack.

